{"title":"向茅盾同志告别","authors":["林焕平"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":4,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"向茅盾同志告别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林焕平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1981年4月10日晚7时看电视，见党和国家领导人及各界群众约二千人，前往北京医院向茅盾同志遗体告别，悲从中来，即成此篇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔年为师长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一新兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新兵变老兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"师业应继承"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小说皆巨制"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史绘典型"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"评论称泰斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舍己育群英"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崇高在精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毕生为人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞠躬至尽瘁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂范于后人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贡献在党国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哲人惊陨落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月失光辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河海翻泪波"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}